Package jakarta.ws.rs.client

Class Entity<T>

java.lang.Object
jakarta.ws.rs.client.Entity<T>
Type Parameters:
T - entity type.
public final class Entity<T>
extends Object
Encapsulates message entity including the associated variant information.
Author:
Marek Potociar
